{"tid":465603,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港人血戰天貓雙11    全球排第二","createTime":"2017-11-11T16:45:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-15T12:31:16.000Z","uid":141461,"like":78,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":78,"replies":[{"pid":"f72b503ba8a82f9d75f0e2106e5ecde699d486a6","tid":465603,"uid":141461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T16:45:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171111/large/1510406940_0ab5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171111%2Flarge%2F1510406940_0ab5.jpg&h=8163f464&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n截至今晚九點，天貓「雙11」成交額破2300億港元新高，除了內地客消費力強勁，亦有賴香港人血戰天貓，因為天貓出口地區排名中，香港第二，僅次俄羅斯，台灣暫為第四。<br />\n<br />\n數據顯示，香港人特別鍾情服裝類產品，最受歡迎產品排名首三位分別是連衣裙、針織衫及衛衣。<br />\n<br />\n港人於「雙11」消費力強勁，按年節節上升，馬雲晚上感謝港人支持。"},{"pid":"1010255b2394291ff1ab0594d7593dc8d9272911","tid":465603,"uid":141461,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T16:50:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6d6d4ee2b00657624b1256f35cd6f2d1ce2769b","tid":465603,"uid":294,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T16:50:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"cd257e3a4618ace57358a3c7c4cac58f5d113a7b","tid":465603,"uid":79563,"like":47,"dislike":4,"score":43,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T16:51:11.000Z","msg":"支港賤種"},{"pid":"3a5bce3aa73541db9673abc4449ca96b165305bc","tid":465603,"uid":1349,"like":85,"dislike":38,"score":47,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T16:51:26.000Z","msg":"乜仲有香港人唔會淘寶？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af9caf432a3290ae6ce1faf15f920af834529754","tid":465603,"uid":693,"like":56,"dislike":3,"score":53,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T16:51:55.000Z","msg":"中國台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal